* Is it a black magic spell
you put me under? *

41:29.279 --> 41:32.916
* This miracle moment *

41:32.916 --> 41:37.020
* Never let it end *

41:37.020 --> 41:40.891
* Every little movement *

41:40.891 --> 41:44.862
* Is beyond improvement *

41:44.862 --> 41:47.664
* You are the magician *

41:47.664 --> 41:52.903
* I've been wishing for
forever *

